# Math grammar — Phase 4
#
# Inline:  $expr$                     (currency-safe delimiter matching)
# Block:   @math [attrs] … @/math
#
# Block attributes:
#   name="…"        title displayed above the equation
#   label="…"        anchor id for @ref() cross-references
#   numbered=false   suppress the (n) equation number (default: numbered)
#   env=align        multi-line, &/\\-separated aligned equations
#
# Reference:  @ref(label)  →  linked (n) pointing at the labeled equation
#
# Expression syntax (subset of LaTeX):
#   \frac{a}{b}  \sqrt{x}  \sqrt[n]{x}  x^n  x_i  x_i^n
#   \sum_{lo}^{hi}  \prod_{lo}^{hi}  \int_{lo}^{hi}  \iint  \iiint  \oint
#   \lim_{x \to a}  \max  \min  \sup  \inf
#   \begin{matrix|pmatrix|bmatrix|vmatrix|Vmatrix|Bmatrix|cases} … \end{…}
#   \left ( … \right )   (also bare "(x)", "[a,b]", "|x|" auto-pair)
#   \vec{v}  \hat{x}  \dot{x}  \tilde{x}  \bar{x}
#   \overline{x}  \underline{x}  \overbrace{x}  \underbrace{x}
#   \mathbf{v}  \boldsymbol{v}  \mathbb{R}
#   \sin \cos \tan \log \ln \exp \gcd \det … (25+ functions, upright)
#   Greek letters, operators, relations, arrows, logic/set symbols
#   (~150 named commands — see src/math-symbols.js)
